==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: HDL
<hw>HDL</hw> <pr>(⟦amac⟧ch`d⟦emac⟧*⟦ecr⟧l")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>High density lipoprotein, a lipoprotein that transports cholesterol
in the blood; high levels are thought to be associated with decreased
risk of coronary heart disease and atherosclerosis; sometimes called
<altname>good cholesterol</altname>. Contrasted with
<contr>LDL</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> high-density lipoprotein.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>He</ent>⟦br⟧
